               <msContents>
                  <summary>Text 1: ff. 1ra-51va: Lives of our fathers and brothers (Inc.: f. 1ra,4-10: ዝንቱ፡ ክፍል፡ ራብዕ፡ እመጽሐፈ፡ ገድሎሙ፡ ወስምዖሙ፡ ለአበዊነ፡ ወአኃዊነ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ለበስያነ፡ መስቀል፡ ዘይትነበብ፡ በወርኀ፡ ሳኔ፡; - "This is the fourth chapter from the Book of the Lives of our holy fathers and brothers who weared the cross, that is read in the month of Sane") Text 2: ff. 52ra-67vb: Life of Bärtälomewos: f. 52rb2-6: ዜና፡ ገድሉ፡ ወስነ፡ ኂሩቱ፡ ለአብ፡ ብፁዕ፡ አቡነ፡ በርተሎሜዎስ፡ መምህረ፡ ንጽሕ። … - "The Story of the combat and beauty of the virtue of our blessed father Bärtälomewos, the teacher of purity"; Text 3: ff. 68ra-104va: f. 68ra7-11: ገድለ፡ ቅዱሳት፡ አንስት። ወምእምናት፡ እለ፡ ወፅአ፡ እምብሔረ፡ ትግራይ። - "Life of the holy and believing women, who came from the land of Təgray"; Text 4: ff. 105ra-138vb; f. 105ra4-10: ክፍል፡ ቀዳሚ፡ … ዘእምገድለ፡ አበዊነ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ ገርዜናውያን፡ - "Chapter 1 … of the Lives of our holy Fathers of Garzen (= Gundä Gunde)"</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     <locus from="1r" to="138v">Fols 1r–138v</locus>
                     <title>Part four of the account of the Esṭifānosite fathers and brothers</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="gez">በስመ ፡ አብ ፡ ወወልድ ፡ ወመንፈስ ፡ ቅዱስ ፡ አሐዱ ፡ አምለክ ። ዝንቱ ፡ ክፍል ፡ ራብዕ ፡ እመጸሐፈ ፡ ገድሎሙ ፡ ወስምዖሙ ። ለአበዊነ ። ወአኃዊነ ፡ ቅዱሳን ፡ ለበስያነ ፡ መስቃል ። ዘይትነበብ ፡ በወርኀ ፡ ሰኔ ። አመ ፡ ፳ወ፭ወበቲ ፡ ካዕበ ፡ በዘተረክበ ፡ ኣዕጽምቲሁ ፡ ለዝንቱ ፡ ብፁዕ ፡ ኣብ ፡ እስጢፋኖስ ፡ ለበሴ ፡ አክሊል ።</incipit>    
                     <note>Acts of the fathers and brothers, fol. 1r-51v; acts of Bartalomēwos, fol. 52r-67v; acts of the nuns, fol. 68r-104v; acts of the Garzēnāweyān fathers , fol. 105r-138v</note>
                     <listBibl type="secondary"><bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/YNI5FTZS"><seg type="thesis"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Teweldeberhan2019Abaw"/><title level="m">Gädlä Abäw wä-Aḫaw [Fourth Part]: Edition and Annotated Translation with Philological and Linguistic Commentary</title><author><t:name xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Teweldeberhan Mezgebe Desta</t:name></author><pubPlace>Addis Ababa</pubPlace><date>2019</date><note type="thesisType">PhD thesis</note></bibl></listBibl>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
